<CONTENT id="_3793152_1"><TITLE value="Session 12"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h4&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884685_1" alt="" width="632" height="355" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Introduction&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyber attacks are a widespread reality in today's world, and they are not going away soon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today we will review what we need to do about it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;News&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2024/300-000-fraud-attempts-blocked-after-optus.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM21613" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;300,000 fraud attempts blocked after Optus breach | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.watoday.com.au/search?text=cyber+security" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Search | WAtoday&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;(cyber security search for West Australian newspaper)&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_24"&gt;Topic&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Cyber attacks and their consequences are very serious.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;During this session we will investigate the nature of typical cyber attacks, and will focus on the following:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Typical attacks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Best in class responses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Best in class preventions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;An attack type that will only get worst -&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/CMHL1bPtQdI?si=Rd_7w-cQKlWlaSYc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Zero-Click Attacks with AI amplification - IBM Technology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Two things this week.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Review the presentation.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Have a look at the data breach at the property giant Meriton.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;What should Meriton do now?&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Portfolio Tasks&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Check assessments tab.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Complete outstanding work&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
